		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Not sure what metal slayer glory is.  But if its on ekrom then you should get a ekrom board.  I would venture to say you'll never get CV3 to work on a mmc3 board.  
<br />
<br />If the game your trying to play is on an ekrom board it should be possible to get it to work by rewiring an elrom board from cv3.  I dont think you'll get much help making repros here though, your best bet is to do the research yourself and figure it out if you really want to make it happen.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


