<br />
<br />I've try like this and it has glitch. 
<br />
<br />CHR:
<br />
<br />bent pin 1 to hole 30    +5V
<br />bent pin 2 to hole 24    A16
<br />bent pin 22 to hole 31  CE
<br />bent pin 24 to hole 2    OE
<br />bent pin 30 to hole 1    A17
<br />
<br />have something wrong?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
