		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />No:
<br />bent pin 22 to hole 31 CE
<br />bent pin 24 to hole 2 OE 
<br />
<br />Yes:
<br />bent pin 24 to hole 31 
<br />bent pin 31 to hole 2

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


